Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:31.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:38.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:45.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:52.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:01:01.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:06.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:11.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:17.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:23.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号为了补给资材 决定前往南极秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相对于即将踏上 人迹未至的大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而感到不安的 娜蒂亚及三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强则一个人显得兴致勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号克服了海底火山 巨大鹦鹉螺的攻击等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,种种大自然的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于由南极大陆下方的 宽阔洞穴中浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.99,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#19 尼莫的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好先进的设备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到南极大陆 竟然存在着这种近代化基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 娜蒂亚 怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好热喔\N好热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这哪是什么 冰天雪地的南极大陆 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好热…\N好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,色狼！\N色狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强你这个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是怪了 南极应该是很冷才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:03:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷到就连穿上那件御寒衣 还是会觉得冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 那是在离这里很远的上方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是靠近地球中间层的地底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们下方就是熔岩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以会比地表要热得多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类从未踏上的冰雪大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是位在巨大地底洞穴的湖畔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯人却在几万年前 就已经建造出这样的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『为了让如此惊人的科学力量』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『在日后派上用场 你能带我四处参观吗？』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算我说不行 你还是会自己跑去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,补给基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那一座座被开挖的小山 也是物资堆起来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由远至近是黄铁、矾土、锰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极大陆是座资源宝库
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾科
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那三根管子和容器 是要做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是石油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是地底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以不是用挖的 而是从上方接油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了\N太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了这些就可以发大财了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你们要怎么拿回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少了鹦鹉螺号根本就办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以男人就是教人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,满脑子就只有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是舰桥 引擎室请说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请报告目前维修情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是引擎室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于诸多部分皆有受损
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还需要15个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要暂时外出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,传令下去在16小时内 完成所有作业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于明晨0700做好出发准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是要去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通知所有作业人员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请于16小时内完成所有作业
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将于明晨0700启航
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轮到玛莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人就得这样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 搞不懂谁才是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 娜蒂亚 穿上御寒衣跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请让我也随行 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 请你们回避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒 要搭这个去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 娜蒂亚 这全都是冰耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们正在冰的隧道里爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才那个是什么 看来很像树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那棵树是世界树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世界树？\N没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撑起天空 树根盘据整个地面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:08:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,传说为一切生命源头的 无比巨大的树木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种地方有结了冰的树木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就表示南极以前 是位在温暖的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么啊 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极大陆可是大得不得了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能会动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 娜蒂亚说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大陆不会移动 只是人类愚昧的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你晓得对科学家来说 最重要的是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你记得世界地图吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 你现在试着回想看看 南北美洲大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及欧洲、非洲大陆的海岸线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不觉得两边的海岸线 可以合而为一吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以密合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是船长 我还是无法相信大陆会移动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以目前十九世纪的科学技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仍无法证明大陆的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 地函热对流迟早会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点也将会获得证明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有的发明与发现 原点都出于自己的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信直觉并加以证明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这才是所谓的科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么没看到船长？\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他带着强与娜蒂亚出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 我想应该是到那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这或许会是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,指南针一直转个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代表这里的地磁场混乱\N强 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在做什么 过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,移动步道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这只是块圆形的板子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看仔细点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 它是浮着的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它的原理为减少地球重力 并利用电磁力前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了不起的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是谁做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两万年前 古代亚特兰提斯人的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这已经变成遗迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快站上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然能减轻重力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是根据怎样的原理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有…有东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像天使一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒觉得那看起来像恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 这里到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是冰雪博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,博物馆？\N博物馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用来保存 在远古时代灭绝的生物们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是刚才那个看起来像是 手持长枪的恐龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是『人龙』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它们是曾建立起 陆地上最大帝国的爬虫类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了配合外界环境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,致使爬虫类体内 以超乎寻常的速度进化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们曾早人类一步 在陆地上建立一大文明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可说是地球的原住民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但它们却因为七千万年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因太阳黑子的变化 所产生的宇宙辐射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从陆地上彻底消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是只有人类才拥有智能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千万不能忘了这点\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生命真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大一扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什么？\N什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像是座冰雪城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里就是目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进去了就会晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见了\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真高兴看到你来 吾友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是怎么回事？ 是谁在说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 娜蒂亚 你们两个到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来介绍 娜蒂亚…抱歉 这两位是娜蒂亚与强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位是我的朋友 伊里恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲸鱼朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲸鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 那是这种生物的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好了不起 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然能和鲸鱼做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟娜蒂亚一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它好像有话想对你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我们说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我到外头等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那怎么行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 你就是娜蒂亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是鲸鱼的你在说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是直接对你的心说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我的心？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要透过蔚蓝之水 这根本是轻而易举的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,透过蔚蓝之水？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你也不需要开口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要在心里想就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟尼莫船长聊完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经跟他道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,道别？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们已经没有机会 再活着见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经活太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的生命也将走到尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,久…是多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我活着的这段期间 地球已经绕过太阳两万圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两万岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以人类的太阳历来计算 就是那么久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你观察人类的历史那么久了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 人类真是种有趣的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类会为了和平而掀起争端 为了争端而破坏和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的是种很有趣的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我将记忆传给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 确实如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然人类是种有趣的生物 但并不愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是那么相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫是我最后的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很感谢他在最后 让我有机会见你们一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他相信你们 并将未来托付到你们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望你们能实现他的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我最后的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人与人的邂逅是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后我来告诉你一件 你很想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所寻找的人就在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后你应该会见到另一位 意想不到的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意想不到的人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？是那样吧？ 我还有个哥哥对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚应该能作个好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了 孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了 蔚蓝之水的继承者们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别走 我还有话要问…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么一直发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水突然发光 然后一下子又熄灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 大概三秒左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 是我在做梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听得懂企鹅话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是 不过这是第一次这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它对我们说『这边请』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要带我们去找尼莫船长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你跟鲸鱼谈过话了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是只有你能和鲸鱼 还有企鹅沟通不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鲸鱼说是因为 我身上有蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们谈了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等我平静一点之后再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们知不知道 尼莫船长上哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有…我是说我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊 那你们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然食物已经补给完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你们还想继续喝汤是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们马上去找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖听话 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怕的女人\N可怕的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生 你是到哪里去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在要到地表
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地表…就是南极大陆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好辽阔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知不觉天已经黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是南极点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好耶 好棒喔 我终于站上南极点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好感动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这只是靠尼莫船长 带我们过来的而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不是靠我自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为鹦鹉螺号 以及古代亚特兰提斯的超科学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们现在才能站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而目前到过这里的人类 还只有我们而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是到了二十世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类应该会凿开流冰 踏上冰层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠自己的力量抵达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信人类具有那样的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,极光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,科学上将这解释为 太阳所发出的电子及质子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与地球的大气碰撞 所造成的发光现象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 光靠那样的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本无法用来形容 这种自然之美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:21:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼泪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所寻找的人就在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冰淇淋？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我发明的全自动冰淇淋制造机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是什么时候做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是为了玛莉而先做好的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到冰淇淋原来这么好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是用南极的冰做成的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.46,0:22:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说这里的冰 在一万二千年前就形成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们正在吃地球的历史啰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地球那么小吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一万二千年是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和这些冰淇淋相比
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类从出生到死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过是短暂的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重点在于要如何度过这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们三个是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们为了找尼莫船长 跑到上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差点被冻成冰棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就穿那样上去吗？\N你们就穿那样上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为下头明明热得很
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是受够那些冰了 (『受够』音近『冰』)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:55.61,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:24:03.72,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:08.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.97,0:24:13.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:22.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:32.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:41.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.17,0:24:45.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.47,0:24:49.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.04,0:24:59.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.03,0:25:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要把强骂得那么惨？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.00,0:25:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.87,0:25:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然是因为强的失败 害我们被长嘴硬鳞鱼号发现
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.17,0:25:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正最后还是会打赢对方 有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.44,0:25:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算让那些孩子 在船上待到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.51,0:25:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最终战争明明就要到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.41,0:25:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『强的失败』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.48,0:25:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
